'''薩利赫·阿里·薩馬德'''（{{lang-ar|صالح علي الصماد}}；{{bd|1979年|1月1日|2018年|4月19日|catIdx=S}}），是一名[[也门|也门]]政治人物，2016年起出任[[胡塞运动|胡塞运动]]政府的[[也门总统|也門最高政治委員會主席]]，並被稱為「[[萨那|萨那]]地區胡塞高級領導人」<ref name="nyt">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/02/11/world/middleeast/yemen-houthi-leader-pledges-to-pursue-power-sharing-accord.html?_r=0|agency=The New York Times|title=U.S. Embassy Shuts in Yemen, Even as Militant Leader Reaches Out|date=10 February 2015|accessdate=10 February 2015|archive-date=2017-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519071016/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/02/11/world/middleeast/yemen-houthi-leader-pledges-to-pursue-power-sharing-accord.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前他曾在2014年9月起擔任[[總統|總統]][[阿卜杜拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪|阿卜杜拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪]]的政治顧問<ref name="endorsed">{{cite news|url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKCN0IX1LF20141113|agency=Reuters|title=Yemen's Houthi group endorse new government: presidential aide|date=13 November 2014|accessdate=10 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150211090452/http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKCN0IX1LF20141113|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年4月19日，薩馬德於[[沙特领导的干预也门行动|沙特聯軍空襲]]中喪生<ref name=bbc20180423>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-43872482 |title=Yemen war: Houthi political leader Saleh al-Sammad 'killed in air raid' |work=BBC News |date=2018-04-23 |accessdate=2018-04-24 |archive-date=2018-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180424032602/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-43872482 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

